mes%20that%20I%20want%20our%20house%20to%20be%20like%20a%20hotel%20%E2%80%94%20nothing%20on%20the%20walls%2C%20very%20plain%20interiors%2C%20no%20clutter%2C%26quot%3B%20Kugizaki%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20envisioned%20very%20minimal%20and%20easy%20spaces%20for%20our%20dream%20home%2C%20preferably%20painted%20inside%20using%20one%20color%20and%20with%20maybe%20one%20statement%20wall.%20That's%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20they%20saw%20The%20Rainbow%20House%20on%20Zillow%2C%20they%20had%20to%20go%20see%20it.%20Stepping%20inside%2C%20the%20couple%20were%20gobsmacked%20by%20the%20sheer%20number%20of%20rainbows.%20The%201%2C028-square-foot%20house%20had%20been%20thoroughly%20hand-painted%20over%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years%20by%20its%20owner%2C%20Patrick%20Hasson.%20Each%20room%20featured%20a%20different%20bright%20color%20with%20hanging%20light%20strings%20to%20match.%20Sixteen%20different%20rainbow%20skulls%20peppered%20the%20interiors.%20The%20garage%2C%20perhaps%20the%20standout%20feature%2C%20showcased%20rainbow%20lines%20that%20spilled%20out%20across%20the%20driveway%20%E2%80%94%20a%20real-life%20version%20of%20the%20unicorn-barfing-rainbows%20meme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20house%20was%20anything%20but%20minimalist%20%E2%80%94%20and%20yet%20it%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20the%20couple.%20%26quot%3BWe%20met%20the%20artist%2C%20who%20actually%20came%20to%20the%20house.%20He%20said%20he%20painted%20the%20house%20this%20way%20to%20bring%20more%20joy%20to%20the%20world.%20That's%20certainly%20what%20we%20felt%20when%20we%20saw%20the%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20told%20me.%20The%20couple%20bought%20it%20for%20%24385%2C000%20and%20plan%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20rainbow%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rainbow%20House%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d5320098114dafd1aaa33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222250%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKugizaki%20and%20Levenhagen%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20quirky%20features%20of%20The%20Rainbow%20House.%3Cp%3EHGTV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKugizaki%20and%20Levenhagen%20aren't%20alone%20in%20their%20unexpected%20love%20for%20a%20kooky%20home.%20In%20fact%2C%20their%20house%20was%20featured%20in%20the%20third%20episode%20of%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhgtv-show-zillow-gone-wild-brings-instagram-account-to-life-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHGTV%20series%20%26quot%3BZillow%20Gone%20Wild%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20tells%20the%20backstories%20of%20unusual%20houses%20people%20just%20purchased%20or%20are%20looking%20to%20sell.%20The%20series%20was%20inspired%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzillowgonewild%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epopular%20Instagram%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20same%20name%20that%20Samir%20Mezrahi%2C%20a%20former%20deputy%20director%20of%20social%20media%20at%20BuzzFeed%2C%20created%20in%20December%202020%20when%20he%20started%20noticing%20weird%20homes%20randomly%20listed%20on%20Zillow.%20%26quot%3BThere%20wasn't%20anything%20for%20the%20casual%20home%20browser%20looking%20for%20these%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me%2C%20so%20he%20began%20sharing%20the%20unique%20houses%20he%20found.%20The%20account%20immediately%20caught%20on%3B%20today%20it%20has%20nearly%202%20million%20followers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20people%20follow%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild%20to%20gawk%20at%20the%20weird%20and%20bizarre%20features%20of%20other%20people's%20homes%2C%20some%20are%20looking%20to%20buy.%20And%20being%20featured%20on%20the%20account%20gives%20listings%20a%20leg%20up.%20Mezrahi%20said%20that%20real-estate%20agents%20actively%20try%20to%20juice%20up%20the%20bizarre%20elements%20of%20their%20homes%20to%20get%20picked%20up.%20%26quot%3BIf%20it's%20around%20Halloween%2C%20for%20example%2C%20agents%20seem%20to%20use%20it%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20cover%20the%20house%20in%20all%20these%20skeletons%20and%20spooky%20decorations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThanks%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhome-sellers-summer-disappointment-mortgage-rates-house-prices-real-estate-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehot%20housing%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-are-new-homes-ugly-construction-builders-design-materials-architecture-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20boredom%20with%20cookie-cutter%20new-builds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there's%20a%20newfound%20fervor%20for%20bizarre%20houses.%20More%20people%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-ditching-sad-beige-interior-design-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Editching%20the%20white%20and%20gray%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%202010s%20modern-farmhouse%20craze%20for%20something%20that%20can%20show%20off%20their%20personal%20style.%20And%20with%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20real-estate%20influencer%20accounts%2C%20a%20wild%20home%20is%20now%20easy%20to%20find.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20homes%20that%20Mezrahi%20features%20aren't%20necessarily%20bad%2C%20ugly%2C%20or%20anything%20built%20in%20bad%20taste.%20These%20are%20not%20the%20over-the-top%20McMansions%20that%20Kate%20Wagner%20shares%20on%20the%20blog%20McMansion%20Hell.%20As%20Mezrahi%20explains%20it%2C%20a%20wild%20house%20just%20needs%20to%20have%20interesting%20or%20quirky%20features%3B%20it's%20the%20customization%20that%20matters.%20He%20cited%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC3a0r-TRQH4%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%253D%253D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20viral%20home%20in%20Gilbert%2C%20Arizona%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20had%20been%20owned%20by%20the%20former%20Los%20Angeles%20Dodger%20Andre%20Ethier%20as%20the%20perfect%20example.%20The%20%2420%20million%20house%20came%20with%20a%20go-kart%20track%2C%20a%20golf%20simulator%2C%20a%20shooting%20range%2C%20a%20built-in%20aquarium%2C%20and%20much%20more.%20Other%20homes%20might%20have%20a%20single%20unique%20element%20like%20the%20giant%20peacock%20mosaic%20in%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6xES_zO9m3%2F%3Fimg_index%3D2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%242%20million%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20San%20Luis%20Obispo%2C%20California%2C%20or%20the%20McDonald's-style%20playroom%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC5oJYuQucSJ%2F%3Fimg_index%3D7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eotherwise%20normal-looking%20%24750%2C000%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Colorado%20Springs%2C%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20standout%20features%20make%20homes%20more%20likely%20to%20go%20viral%2C%20leading%20to%20more%20exposure%20and%20possibly%20a%20higher%20selling%20price.%20Nick%20Leyendecker%2C%20the%20founder%20and%20principal%20broker%20at%20Leyendecker%20Luxury%20Real%20Estate%2C%20said%20that%20if%20maximizing%20the%20sale%20price%20is%20the%20primary%20objective%2C%20the%20more%20attention%20a%20property%20receives%20from%20potential%20buyers%2C%20the%20higher%20the%20probability%20of%20success.%20When%20trying%20to%20sell%20a%20home%2C%20most%20real-estate%20agents%20try%20to%20garner%20attention%20in%20three%20ways%3A%20paid%20ads%2C%20organic%20sharing%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20earned%20media%20from%20news%20outlets%20%E2%80%94%20aka%20%26quot%3Borganic%20attention%20on%20steroids%2C%26quot%3B%20Leyendecker%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20too%20much%20exposure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHomeowners%20with%20highly%20customized%20spaces%20often%20ask%20Mezrahi%20to%20feature%20their%20homes%20before%20they're%20even%20on%20the%20market.%20%26quot%3BThe%20homeowner%20that%20converted%20their%20swimming%20pool%20into%20a%20man%20cave%20was%20one%20that%20comes%20to%20mind%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20And%20when%20homes%20get%20featured%2C%20they%20often%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20April%2C%20Leyendecker%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC6UQJeLu81j%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20listing%20in%20Plymouth%2C%20Minnesota%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild.%20The%20house%20was%20decked%20out%20with%20flashy%2C%20customized%20designs%20including%20a%20secret%20room%20behind%20a%20classic%20Coca-Cola%20machine%20door.%20Within%20two%20months%2C%20it%20sold%20for%20%242.8%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20new%20trend%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20previous%20wisdom%20that%20weird%20houses%20don't%20sell.%20When%20Hasson%2C%20the%20previous%20owner%20of%20The%20Rainbow%20House%2C%20was%20preparing%20to%20place%20the%20home%20on%20the%20market%2C%20his%20real-estate%20agent%20warned%20him%20not%20to%20have%20high%20expectations.%20%26quot%3BMy%20real-estate%20agent%20was%20like%2C%20'It's%20a%20rainbow%20house%20and%20not%20the%20easiest%20to%20sell%2C'%26quot%3B%20Hasson%20told%20The%20Desert%20Sun.%20But%20then%20the%20listing%20was%20shared%20on%20TikTok%20and%20blew%20up.%20Within%20two%20months%20of%20being%20listed%2C%20it%20sold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EInterest%20in%20outrageous%20homes%20has%20begun%20to%20expand%20beyond%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild.%20A%20surge%20of%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F24-year-old-miami-realtor-uses-tiktok-find-clients-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal-estate%20influencers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffredrik-eklund-social-media-advice-for-real-estate-agents-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal-estate%20accounts%3C%2Fa%3E%20showing%20off%20unique%20homes%20have%20cropped%20up.%20In%20a%20recent%20Zillow%20survey%2C%20respondents%20said%20that%20if%20cost%20weren't%20a%20factor%2C%20they%20would%20want%20a%20home%20with%20whimsical%20features%20they%20had%20dreamed%20of%20as%20a%20child%3A%2076%25%20said%20they%20would%20want%20a%20home%20theater%2C%2043%25%20pined%20for%20a%20bowling%20alley%2C%20and%2058%25%20wanted%20their%20own%20personal%20elevator.%20The%20study%20also%20found%20that%20different%20generations%20favored%20different%20features.%20For%20example%2C%2038%25%20of%20those%20born%20in%20the%20'50s%20dream%20of%20a%20home%20with%20a%20white%20picket%20fence%2C%20whereas%20only%2021%25%20of%20those%20born%20in%20the%20'90s%20shared%20the%20same%20vision.%20Millennials%20preferred%20a%20hot%20tub%20and%20an%20elevator%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-millennials-more-optimistic-about-buying-home-inflation-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emillennials%20are%20able%20to%20buy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20those%20with%20the%20cash%20to%20spend%20are%20making%20those%20dreams%20a%20reality.%20And%20at%20a%20time%20when%20more%20people%20see%20into%20your%20home%20via%20social%20media%2C%20having%20cool%20features%20you%20can%20show%20off%20is%20a%20major%20bonus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAshley%20Spencer%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20both%20in%20their%2030s%2C%20were%20looking%20for%20an%20eye-catching%20midcentury-modern%20home%20at%20the%20end%20of%202021%20when%20they%20stumbled%20across%20one%20featured%20on%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild.%20The%20house's%20interiors%20were%20covered%20in%20floor-to-ceiling%20tile%20%E2%80%94%20a%20showroom%20for%20the%20previous%20owners'%20tile%20business.%20%26quot%3BFor%20us%2C%20it's%20really%20the%20Mid%20Mod%20architecture%20that%20drew%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Spencer%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20house%20was%20just%20so%20unique%20with%20all%20the%20colors%2C%20and%20outside%20the%20home%20is%20shaped%20like%20a%20bow%20tie%20because%20it%20was%20built%20on%20such%20a%20thin%20lot.%20The%20home%20has%20really%20cool%20angles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20loved%20that%20the%20home%20was%20in%20the%20woods%20and%20next%20to%20a%20lake.%20They%20traveled%20from%20Austin%20to%20Minneapolis%20to%20see%20it%20for%20themselves%20and%20made%20an%20offer%20the%20next%20day.%20Within%20a%20month%2C%20they%20closed%20on%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20guests%20come%20over%2C%20Spencer%20loves%20to%20show%20off%20her%201955%20home's%20built-in%20shuffleboard%20court.%20%26quot%3BI've%20never%20seen%20anything%20like%20it%20anywhere%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20Her%20guests%20are%20always%20amused%20to%20discover%20the%20home%20was%20listed%20on%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild.%20%26quot%3BMy%20husband%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20more%20reserved%20and%20nervous%20about%20sharing%20that%20the%20house%20was%20from%20Zillow%20Gone%20Wild.%20But%20I%20have%20no%20problem%20talking%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20not%20every%20wild%20home%20will%20be%20loved%20by%20everyone.%20But%20Leyendecker%20said%20that%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcoolest-homes-on-the-planet-2016-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunique%20homes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20always%20a%20matter%20of%20finding%20the%20right%20person.%20%26quot%3BMarketing%20exposure%20is%20just%20one%20piece%20of%20the%20puzzle%20%E2%80%94%20homes%20are%20a%20very%20personal%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BEven%20the%20most%20broadly%20marketable%20properties%20imaginable%20are%20a%20good%20fit%20for%20some%20buyers%20and%20a%20bad%20fit%20for%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20old%20saying%20suggests%2C%20beauty%20is%20in%20the%20eye%20of%20the%20beholder.%20The%20beholders%20are%20just%20getting%20more%20ambitious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rainbow%20House%20garage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d5337268f62ba18a868e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E'The%20Rainbow%20House%20was%20a%20dream%20we%20didn't%20know%20we%20always%20had%2C'%20Levenhagen%20said.%3Cp%3EHGTV%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20their%20part%2C%20Kugizaki%20and%20Levenhagen%20don't%20plan%20on%20ever%20selling%20their%20wild%20rainbow%20house.%20They%20feel%20like%20stewards%20of%20the%20home%20and%20promised%20the%20former%20owner%20that%20they%20would%20keep%20everything%20the%20same.%20%26quot%3BHe%20really%20wanted%20to%20make%20sure%20someone%20wasn't%20going%20to%20buy%20it%20and%20then%20keep%20the%20rainbow%20garage%20but%20then%20paint%20everything%20else%20over%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Levenhagen.%20The%20couple%20agree%20that%20rainbows%20mean%20a%20lot%20to%20people%20for%20many%20different%20reasons.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20important%20to%20a%20lot%20of%20communities%20including%20the%20LGBTQ%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kugizaki.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20in%20some%20ways%20just%20a%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20Levenhagen%20added%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20guess%20you%20could%20say%20The%20Rainbow%20House%20was%20a%20dream%20we%20didn't%20know%20we%20always%20had.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fmichelle-mastro%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMichelle%20Mastro%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20covers%20lifestyle%2C%20travel%2C%20architecture%2C%20and%20culture.%20When%20she's%20not%20researching%20or%20writing%2C%20she's%20hiking%20trails%20(badly).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzillow-gone-wild-weird-unique-houses-homes-hot-homebuying-selling-2024-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720604642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F668d869e39de72f47bc9c476%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business