%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezos-amazon-business-advice-applies-to-ai-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20built%20its%20delivery%20chops%20for%20years.%20In%20fact%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eone%20big%20selling%20point%20of%20its%20%24139-a-year%20Prime%20membership%20is%20free%20one-day%20shipping%20to%20customers'%20doors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Day%20promotions%20are%20pointing%20shoppers%20toward%20the%20option%20of%20taking%20on%20some%20of%20the%20delivery%20work%20themselves%20by%20instead%20collecting%20packages%20from%20its%20growing%20network%20of%20lockers%20and%20other%20pick-up%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPrime%20members%20are%20%26quot%3Bable%20to%20choose%20how%20and%20where%20those%20items%20arrive%E2%80%94%20whether%20at%20home%2C%20work%2C%20or%20places%20you%20frequent%20with%20Amazon's%20network%20of%20thousands%20of%20package%20pick-up%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20said%20last%20month%20as%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpress.aboutamazon.com%2F2024%2F6%2Famazons-10th-prime-day-event-returns-july-16-17-with-millions-of-exclusive-deals-for-prime-members%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etouted%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20massive%20shopping%20event%2C%20which%20is%20scheduled%20for%20July%2016%20and%2017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon%20has%20been%20adding%20pick-up%20points%20in%20recent%20years.%20Its%20locker%20banks%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20are%20common%20sites%20in%20apartment%20lobbies%2C%20college%20dorms%2C%20convenience%20stores%2C%20and%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmpdc.dc.gov%2Frelease%2Fmpd-expands-amazon-lockers-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epolice%20stations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20also%20staffed%20Amazon%20Counters%20at%20Whole%20Foods%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20Amazon%20offers%20%26quot%3Btens%20of%20thousands%20of%20package%20pick-up%20locations%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20U.S.%20The%20spokesperson%20also%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aboutamazon.com%2Fnews%2Foperations%2Fhow-to-use-amazon-locker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20blog%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20last%20year%2C%20which%20says%20that%20items%20ordered%20for%20pick-up%20at%20lockers%20must%20be%20fulfilled%20by%20Amazon%20and%20weigh%20under%2010%20pounds%2C%20among%20other%20requirements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20picking%20up%20parcels%20might%20seem%20contrary%20to%20Amazon%20Prime's%20noted%20quick-shipping%20benefits%2C%20it's%20could%20be%20useful%20both%20for%20the%20customer%20and%20for%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20shoppers%20already%20go%20to%20Amazon's%20stores%20or%20other%20places%20with%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Famazon-locker%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20locker%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it's%20quite%20convenient%2C%20said%20Jeremy%20Bartlow%2C%20a%20partner%20and%20consumer%20expert%20at%20PA%20Consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20sitting%20there%20in%20the%20locker%20on%20the%20way%20home%20or%20at%20the%20grocery%20store%2C%20wherever%20I'm%20stopping%2C%26quot%3B%20Bartlow%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20especially%20convenient%20to%20get%20an%20order%20delivered%20to%20a%20locker%20if%20you've%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-hub-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmazon%20packages%20stolen%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20your%20porch%20or%20apartment%20mailroom%2C%20or%20if%20you're%20ordering%20an%20expensive%20item%20and%20want%20the%20extra%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20reason%20why%20Amazon%20would%20love%20for%20you%20to%20pick%20up%20your%20Prime%20Day%20deals%20instead%20of%20delivering%20them%20to%20your%20front%20door%3A%20their%20bottom%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmazon's%20annual%20spending%20on%20shipping%20has%