3Cp%3EI've%20had%20to%20stop%20chatting%20with%20some%20people%20I%20wanted%20to%20date%20just%20because%20I%20know%20they%20won't%20fit%20in%20my%20geographical%20area%20restriction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220418f15f-d937-44aa-8c56-2dce7def7e20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhile%20working%20here%2C%20I%20did%20meet%20someone%2C%20and%20it%20was%20going%20smoothly%20until%20last%20year%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20dating%20a%20woman%20who%20lived%20in%20Boston%20for%20a%20while%2C%20but%20I%20couldn't%20visit%20her%20often%20after%20I%20had%20to%20return%20to%20the%20office.%20We%20tried%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-only-been-long-distance-relationships-whole-life-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elong-distance%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20that%20wasn't%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20spark%20and%20chemistry%20died%20%E2%80%94%20when%20you%20aren't%20with%20each%20other%20daily%2C%20you%20start%20drifting.%20We%20also%20had%20arguments%20and%20differences%20of%20opinion%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20reduction%20of%20sexual%20or%20romantic%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20knew%20the%20relationship%20would%20end%20even%20though%20I%20said%20it%20could%20work%20out.%20With%20layoffs%20looming%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20the%20luxury%20of%20choosing%20her%20over%20my%20career%2C%20which%20was%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f53b1d6-ad30-463f-8974-234272d8880d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20noticed%20women%20care%20about%20a%20company's%20brand%20name%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20get%20much%20more%20attention%20now%20than%20before%20I%20had%20my%20Big%20Tech%20job%20and%20lived%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20and%20I%20can%20tell%20it's%20because%20I%20work%20for%20a%20FAANG%20company.%20It%20feels%20like%20most%20girls%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20are%20sussing%20guys%20out%20based%20on%20their%20educational%20background%2C%20earning%20potential%