c%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20won%20nine%20seats%2C%20three%20less%20than%20the%20last%20time%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20won%20five%2C%20three%20more%20than%20the%20previous%20election.%20In%20terms%20of%20vote%20share%2C%20the%20NDA%20received%2047%25%20votes%2C%20while%20INDIA%20got%2039%25%2C%20reducing%20the%20former's%20lead%20from%2024%20percentage%20points%20(pp)%20in%202019%20to%20just%208%20pp%20in%202024.%20In%20terms%20of%20assembly%20segments%2C%20the%20NDA%20was%20leading%20in%2052%20seats%20(11%20less%20than%20the%20last%20time)%2C%20and%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%2029%20seats%20(11%20more).%20The%20total%20house%20strength%20is%2081.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20INDIA%20bloc%20won%20all%20the%20ST-reserved%20seats%20(Khunti%2C%20Singhbhum%2C%20Lohardaga%2C%20Dumka%2C%20and%20Rajmahal)%20this%20time.%20In%20contrast%2C%20in%202019%2C%20the%20NDA%20had%20won%20three%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20while%20the%20United%20Progressive%20Alliance%20(UPA)%20got%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NDA's%20performance%20was%20hampered%20by%20the%20Congress's%20narrative%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20alter%20the%20Constitution%20if%20it%20comes%20to%20power%2C%20as%20also%20by%20allegations%20of%20tampering%20with%20Santhal%20Pargana%20and%20the%20Chhota%20Nagpur%20Tenancy%20Act.%20The%20public%20sympathy%20generated%20by%20Soren's%20arrest%20only%20helped%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20further%2C%20denting%20the%20NDA's%20prospects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20To%20Expect%20In%20Assembly%20Polls%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20assembly%20elections%20this%20year%20are%20expected%20to%20witness%20a%20keen%20contest%20between%20the%20NDA%20and%20INDIA.%20They%20will%20be%20much%20more%20localised%20than%20the%20general%20elections.%20Also%2C%20as%20per%20past%20trends%2C%20the%20BJP%20may%20see%20a%20dip%20in%20its%20vote%20share%20compared%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20In%202014%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20the%20BJP's%20vote%20dipped%20by%205%20pp%20in%20state%20elections%2C%20while%20in%202019%2C%20this%20drop%20was%20a%20whopping%2019%20pp.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20government%20faces%20challenges%20too.%20Natural%20anti-incumbency%20is%20one.%20Then%2C%20the%20BJP%20hopes%20that%20the%20raids%20against%20a%20few%20MLAs%20and%20close%20associates%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20may%20have%20harmed%20the%20image%20of%20the%20government%2C%20especially%20amongst%20urban%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20JMM%20is%20banking%20on%20a%20possible%20sympathy%20wave%20for%20Soren%20and%20anger%20against%20the%20BJP.%20This%20was%20visible%20to%20some%20extent%20in%20the%20recently%20concluded%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20voting%20pattern%20of%20the%20SCs%2C%20STs%20and%20Muslims%20will%20be%20a%20key%20thing%20to%20watch.%20The%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20trying%20to%20create%20a%20consolidated%20base%20in%20their%20favour%20as%20these%20three%20groups%20account%20for%2050%25%20of%20the%20state's%20population.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20And%20BJP%20Units%20Unhappy%20With%20Their%20Chiefs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20section%20of%20the%20state's%20Congress%20leaders%20is%20unhappy%20with%20the%20functioning%20and%20performance%20of%20its%20state%20chief%20Rajesh%20Thakur%2C%20and%20has%20been%20demanding%20his%20replacement%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20If%20this%20happens%20before%20the%20election%2C%20the%20new%20President%20will%20not%20have%20enough%20time%20to%20prepare%20for%20the%20polls.%20Also%2C%20two%20sitting%20ministers%20have%20been%20replaced%20in%20the%20Congress's%20quota%2C%20and%20this%20could%20intensify%20factionalism%20in%20the%20state%20unit.%20Soren%20has%20dropped%20his%20brother%20Basant%20from%20the%20Cabinet%20this%20time%2C%20and%20this%20could%20lead%20to%20a%20family%20feud.%20Earlier%2C%20Soren's%20sister-in-law%2C%20Seeta%20Soren%2C%20had%20left%20the%20party%20and%20joined%20the%20BJP%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20-%20though%20she%20lost%20the%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20BJP%20front%2C%20with%20the%20party%20losing%20all%20five%20ST%20seats%2C%20there%20were%20calls%20for%20the%20removal%20of%20state%20president%20Babulal%20Marandi.%20Opponents%20cite%20his%20thin%20appeal%20amongst%20STs%2C%20and%20this%20could%20cost%20the%20party%20dearly%20in%20the%20upcoming%20state%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETribal%20Pride%20And%20BJP's%20Key%20Challenge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETribal%20or%20adivasi%20pride%20will%20be%20a%20big%20factor%20too%2C%20given%20that%20a%20large%20share%20of%20tribals%20see%20the%20JMM%20as%20the%20only%20party%20representing%20them%20and%20their%20issues.%20The%20BJP%20so%20far%20has%20had%20little%20success%20in%20wooing%20STs%20-%20it%20won%20only%20two%20of%20the%2028%20ST-reserved%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20polls%20-%20despite%20its%20wide%20outreach%20programmes.%20These%20included%20putting%20up%20a%20tribal%20candidate%20for%20the%20presidential%20elections%2C%20the%20appointment%20of%20Marandi%2C%20celebrating%20Birsa%20Munda's%20birth%20anniversary%20as%20Janjatiya%20Gaurav%20Diwas%2C%20and%20a%20package%20of%20Rs%2024%2C000%20crore%20for%20vulnerable%20tribal%20groups.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20facing%20ally%20troubles.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20perceptible%20decline%20in%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20All%20Jharkhand%20Students%20Union%20(AJSU)%2C%20and%20the%20simultaneous%20rise%20of%20parties%20like%20the%20Jharkhandi%20Bhasha%20Khatiyan%20Sangharsh%20Samiti%20(JBKSS)%2C%20led%20by%2029-year-old%20Jairam%20Kumar%20Mahato%2C%20threatens%20to%20sway%20the%20Kurmi%20vote.%20The%20JBKSS%20has%20already%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20contest%20the%20majority%20of%20the%2081%20seats.%20Many%20Kurmis%20are%20also%20reportedly%20unhappy%20over%20the%20denial%20of%20a%20cabinet%20berth%20to%20the%20AJSU%20leader%20who%20won%20from%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20main%20challenge%20is%20wooing%20the%20STs%2C%20and%20unless%20it%20devises%20a%20strategy%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20it%20will%20face%20an%20uphill%20task%20in%20the%20state%20elections.%20To%20sum%20up%2C%20while%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20gets%20a%20boost%20with%20Soren's%20release%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20need%20to%20relook%20its%20strategy%20to%20reclaim%20Jharkhand%20from%20the%20JMM-led%20coalition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Amitabh%20Tiwari%20is%20a%20political%20strategist%20and%20commentator.%20In%20his%20earlier%20avatar%2C%20he%20was%20a%20corporate%20and%20investment%20banker.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720601760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fchc1445o_hemant-soren_625x300_10_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjharkhand-polls-can-bjp-survive-a-sympathy-wave-for-hemant-soren-6074473%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP's%20main%20challenge%20is%20wooing%20the%20STs%2C%20and%20unless%20it%20devises%20a%20strategy%20to%20win%20a%20majority%20of%20these%20seats%2C%20it%20will%20face%20an%20uphill%20task%20in%20the%20state%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjharkhand-polls-can-bjp-survive-a-sympathy-wave-for-hemant-soren-6074473%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjharkhand-polls-can-bjp-survive-a-sympathy-wave-for-hemant-soren-6074473%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fjharkhand-polls-can-bjp-survive-a-sympathy-wave-for-hemant-soren-6074473%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BLACKPINK's%20Lisa%20breaks%20YouTube%20re