h-an-exquisite-diamond-choti-for-anant-ambani-and-radhika-merchants-garba-night%2Farticleshow%2F111628487.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Joint%20Accounts%2C%20ATM%20Access%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20Underlines%20Homemakers'%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20time%20has%20come%20for%20Indian%20men%20to%20recognise%20the%20indispensable%20role%20played%20by%20homemakers%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20they%20make%20for%20the%20family%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20observation%20came%20as%20a%20bench%20of%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20and%20Justice%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20ruled%20that%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmuslim-women-entitled-to-alimony-on-divorce-rules-supreme-court-6073157%5C%22%3Edivorced%20Muslim%20woman%20can%20seek%20alimony%20from%20her%20husband%20under%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bench%20held%20that%20the%20law%20for%20seeking%20maintenance%20applies%20to%20all%20married%20women%2C%20irrespective%20of%20their%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20the%20key%20role%20of%20homemakers%20in%20the%20family%2C%20the%20court%20said%20it%20is%20necessary%20for%20husbands%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20to%20their%20wives.%20%26quot%3BWe%20highlight%20the%20necessity%20for%20husbands%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20to%20their%20wives...%20practical%20measures%20such%20as%20maintaining%20joint%20bank%20accounts%20and%20sharing%20ATM%20access%20to%20ensure%20economic%20stability%20for%20women%20within%20the%20household%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20order%20stating%20that%20a%20Muslim%20woman%20is%20entitled%20to%20maintenance%20from%20her%20husband%20after%20divorce%20under%20Section%20125%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20underlined%20that%20maintenance%20is%20not%20charity%20but%20a%20fundamental%20right%20of%20married%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20right%20transcends%20religious%20boundaries%2C%20reinforcing%20the%20principle%20of%20gender%20equality%20and%20financial%20security%20for%20all%20married%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESection%20125%20broadly%20says%20a%20person%20with%20sufficient%20means%20cannot%20deny%20maintenance%20to%20their%20wife%2C%20children%20or%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judgment%20has%20come%20on%20a%20petition%20by%20Mohd%20Abdul%20Samad%2C%20who%20was%20directed%20by%20a%20family%20court%20to%20pay%20a%20monthly%20allowance%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20to%20his%20divorced%20wife.%20Mr%20Samad%20had%20challenged%20the%20direction%20in%20Telangana%20High%20Court%2C%20which%20modified%20the%20amount%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000.%20He%20then%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20His%20counsel%20argued%20that%20divorced%20Muslim%20women%20can%20seek%20recourse%20to%20the%20Muslim%20Women%20(Protection%20of%20Rights%20on%20Divorce)%20Act%2C%201986%20Act%20and%20stressed%20that%20it%20provides%20much%20more%20than%20what%20Section%20125%20CrPC%20does.%20He%20also%20argued%20that%20a%20special%20law%20--%20referring%20to%20the%20Act%20--%20shall%20prevail%20over%20a%20general%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmicus%20Curiae%20Gaurav%20Agarwal%20countered%20that%20the%20personal%20law%20does%20not%20take%20away%20a%20woman's%20entitlement%20to%20relief%20under%20the%20gender-neutral%20CrPC.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720598040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fdbuvihn_supreme-court-istock_625x300_02_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-joint-accounts-atm-access-supreme-court-underlines-homemakers-rights-6074023%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20time%20has%20come%20for%20Indian%20men%20to%20recognise%20the%20indispensable%20role%20played%20by%20homemakers%20and%20the%20sacrifices%20they%20make%20for%20the%20family%2C%20