0Bengal%20was%20not%20maintainable%20and%20said%20the%20case%20would%20have%20a%20huge%20impact%20on%20federalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20considered%20the%20DSPE%20(Delhi%20Special%20Police%20Establishment)%20Act%20and%20Supreme%20Court%20rules.%20It%20cannot%20be%20said%20that%20West%20Bengal%20has%20not%20made%20out%20any%20case%20against%20Centre%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20section%206%20of%20the%20DSPE%20Act%2C%201946%2C%20the%20CBI%20must%20obtain%20consent%20from%20respective%20state%20governments%20to%20conduct%20investigations%20in%20their%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DSPE%20Act%20provides%20immunity%20from%20the%20Centre's%20powers%2C%20the%20court%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20find%20that%20in%20the%20present%20suit%2C%20the%20plaintiff%20is%20raising%20the%20legal%20issue%20of%20whether%20CBI%20can%20file%20a%20case%20under%20the%20DSPE%20Act%20after%20revocation%20of%20consent.%20Can%20CBI%20register%20and%20investigate%20cases%20in%20violation%20of%20Section%206%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20hearing%20is%20on%20August%2013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20currently%20probing%20multiple%20charges%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20land%20grabbing%2C%20and%20ration%20scam%20against%20Shahjahan%20Sheikh%20-%20a%20former%20Trinamool%20leader%20and%20local%20strongman%20-%20and%20his%20aides%20in%20Bengal's%20Sandeshkhali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20government%20had%20opposed%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court's%20CBI%20probe%20into%20the%20case.%20Allowing%20the%20CBI%20to%20continue%20its%20probe%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20wondered%20why%20the%20Bengal%20government%20was%20interested%20in%20protecting%20an%20individual.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1720595640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fbs64jvlo_sandeshkhali-violence_625x300_02_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%