20glacier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh%20was%20posted%20with%2026%20Punjab%20as%20a%20medical%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECaptain%20Singh%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flove-at-first-sight-captain-anshuman-singhs-widow-smriti-singh-recalls-how-they-met-6046602%5C%22%3Egiven%20the%20award%20posthumously%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20wife%20Smriti%20and%20mother%20received%20it%20from%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20users%20posted%20emotional%20tribute%20to%20the%20soldier%2C%20one%20user%20posted%20a%20disrespectful%20comment%2C%20which%20has%20been%20termed%20%26quot%3Blewd%26quot%3B%20by%20NCW%20in%20its%20letter%20to%20Delhi%20Police%20Commissioner%20Sanjay%20Arora.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ENational%20Commission%20for%20Women%20(NCW)%20has%20identified%20a%20lewd%20and%20derogatory%20comment%20made%20by%20Ahmad%20K.%20from%20Delhi%20on%20a%20photo%20of%20a%20Kirt%20Chakra%20Captain%20Anshuman%20Singh's%20widow.%20This%20act%20violates%20Section%2079%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%2C%20and%20Section%2067%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fh2zvqfKGgy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fh2zvqfKGgy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20NCW%20(%40NCWIndia)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FNCWIndia%2Fstatus%2F1810261971213701367%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%208%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20also%20said%20that%20the%20man%20named%20Ahmad%20K%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Delhi%2C%20made%20the%20comment%20that%20contravenes%20Section%2079%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%2C%202023%2C%20and%20Section%2067%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act%2C%202000.%20%26quot%3BNCW%20condemns%20this%20behaviour%20and%20urges%20immed