hem%3B%20Raised%201.5%20Cr%20in%20Funding%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDid%20you%20know%20that%20in%20India%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheweek.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-news%2Fsouth-and-central-asia%2F957065%2Fwhy-animal-human-conflict-is-on-the-rise-in-india%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Week%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20between%202018%20and%202020%2C%20about%201%2C401%20humans%20and%20301%20elephants%20were%20killed%20due%20to%20conflicts%E2%80%8B%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Maharashtra%20alone%2C%20tiger%20attacks%20caused%2086%20deaths%20in%202021%20and%20105%20in%202022%E2%80%8B.%20While%20these%20might%20seem%20like%20mere%20numbers%2C%20animal%20conflict%20is%20a%20rising%20concern%20among%20farmers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman-animal%20conflict%20%3C%2Fa%3Ehas%20been%20a%20lingering%20issue%20for%20decades.%20Human%20encroachment%20on%20forest%20land%20has%20been%20a%20rising%20trend%20leaving%20animals%20astray.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20is%20increased%20animal%20activity%20in%20human%20settlements.%20The%20ones%20paying%20the%20most%20for%20this%20are%20farmers%20and%20landowners%20living%20around%20the%20fringes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20question%20of%20who-is-endangering-and-encroaching-on-whose-space%20prevails%2C%20farmers%20in%20regions%20like%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Gujarat%20face%20heavy%20losses%20due%20to%20animal%20encroachment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20innovations%20to%20keep%20animals%20at%20bay%20have%20been%20developed%20by%20companies%20all%20across%20the%20country%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20who%20aim%20at%20scaring%20the%20animals%20away%20without%20the%20intention%20of%20hurting%20them.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CKatidhan%20aims%20to%20help%20farmers%20mitigate%20their%20losses%20while%20keeping%20the%20animals%20at%20a%20distance.%20We%20study%20their%20movements%20and%20use%20technology%20to%20scare%20the%20animals%20from%20human%20settlements%2C%E2%80%9D%20S%20R%20Ayan%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20the%20Bengaluru-based%20startup%2C%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKatidhan%20helps%20farmers%20reduce%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F232462%2Fifs-hero-elephant-safety-fence-electric-uttarakhand-haldwani-man-animal-elephant-conflict-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20wildlife-related%20losses%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20their%20innovative%20products%20aimed%20at%20a%20harmless%20resolution%20of%20such%20conflicts.%20The%20startup%20was%20also%20featured%20on%20a%20Shark%20Tank%20episode%20in%20season%203%2C%20bagging%20a%20deal%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EInnovations%20that%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ayan%20is%20a%20robotics%20engineer%20who%20worked%20on%20building%20consumer%20robots.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20working%20in%20the%20city%20when%20a%20friend%20highlighted%20the%20issue%20of%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F175235%2Fassam-wildlife-conservation-dulu-borah-elephant-man-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20human-wildlife%20conflict.%20%3C%2Fa%3EHe%20explained%20how%20this%20issue%20exists%20and%20has%20been%20resulting%20in%20losses%2C%20and%20I%20was%20quite%20taken%20aback%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20further%20research%2C%20Ayan%20realised%20the%20depth%20of%20the%20issue%20and%20how%20it%20is%20prevalent%20in%20most%20states%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20bid%20to%20protect%20their%20fields%2C%20farmers%20would%20resort%20to%20things%20like%20electric%20fencing%20which%20could%20potentially%20hurt%20the%20animals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ayan%20wanted%20to%20help%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20wild-life-related%20losses.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-7-1720534655-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356163%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAyan%20wanted%20to%20help%20farmers%20suffering%20from%20wild-life-related%20losses.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20brain%20got%20into%20problem-solving%20mode%20and%20the%20idea%20of%20Katidhan%20was%20born.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20area%20needed%20more%20solutions%20that%20did%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20newer%20projects%20to%20work%20on%20and%20this%20felt%20like%20a%20perfect%20opportunity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20Ayan%20set%20out%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20and%20collected%20a%20small%20team%20of%20scientists%20and%20engineers%20to%20develop%20an%20animal-friendly%20resolution.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20more%20I%20spoke%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20different%20regions%20during%20the%20initial%20stages%20of%20the%20project%2C%20the%20more%20I%20realised%20how%20small-scale%20farmers%20suffer%20more%20due%20to%20animal%20attacks.%20They%20sometimes%20lose%20more%20than%2015%20percent%20of%20their%20crop%20due%20to%20animal%20attacks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20really%20sympathise%20with%20their%20situation%20and%20wanted%20to%20help%20them%20and%20save%20the%20animals%20from%20cruel%20devices%20too.%20I%20could%20see%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20starving%20for%20innovations%20and%20I%20thus%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20Katidhan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20products%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20that%20all%20their%20products%20are%20non-invasive%2C%20Ayan%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20products%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20designed%20to%20deter%20animals%20without%20causing%20any%20physical%20harm.%20They%20work%20by%20altering%20behavioural%20patterns%20to%20scare%20the%20animals%20away.%20This%20is%20crucial%20because%20current%20methods%2C%20like%20electric%20fences%2C%20can%20harm%20animals%20and%20even%20unsuspecting%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20offer%20two%20versions%20of%20their%20deterrent%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20our%20main%20products%20is%20a%20solar-powered%20auto%20light%2C%20effective%20against%20various%20wild%20animals%20such%20as%20elephants%2C%20wild%20boars%2C%20and%20tigers.%20It%20is%20called%20Parabraksh.%20This%20product%20operates%20automatically%2C%20flashing%20in%20different%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%20creating%20the%20illusion%20of%20another%20animal%20in%20the%20area%2C%20which%20deters%20these%20animals%20from%20entering%20the%20fields%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20solar-powered%20autonomous%20light%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20operates%20automatically%2C%20switching%20on%20at%20sunset%20and%20flashing%20in%20various%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20night%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20LED%20light%20itself%20isn%E2%80%99t%20inherently%20threatening.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20way%20the%20system%20is%20designed%20to%20be%20perceived%20by%20the%20animals%20that%20makes%20it%20effective.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20significant%20product%20that%20the%20company%20offers%20is%20the%20bioplastic%20scare%20system%2C%20which%20they%20call%20Kaapikat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20the%20products%20provided%20by%20the%20startup%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Flobo-8-1720534857-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-356166%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAll%20the%20products%20provided%20by%20the%20startup%20are%20non-invasive%20and%20do%20not%20harm%20the%20animals.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20uses%20sensors%20to%20detect%20motion%20and%20plays%20different%20animal%20sounds%20to%20keep%20them%20away%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20monkeys.%20However%2C%20monkeys%20are%20very%20smart%20and%20their%20behaviour%20varies%20by%20region%2C%20so%20we%20only%20sell%20this%20product%20selectively%20and%20encourage%20farmers%20to%20test%20it%20in%20their%20area%20before%20making%20a%20larger%20purchase%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20offer%20customised%20solutions%20combining%20light%20and%20sound%20deterrents%20for%20specific%20needs.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20flexibility%20allows%20us%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20types%20of%20wildlife%20and%20their%20unique%20behaviours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%982000%2B%20farmers%20benefitted%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20they%20faced%20initially%2C%20Ayan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20team%20consists%20of%204%20to%205%20dedicated%20members%2C%20and%20it%20took%20us%20about%20two-and-a-half%20years%20to%20develop%20these%20products.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnderstanding%20the%20behaviour%20of%20different%20animals%20and%20how%20it%20changes%20with%20the%20seasons%20was%20crucial.%20For%20instance%2C%20elephants%20and%20wild%20boars%20behave%20differently%20in%20the%20winter%20compared%20to%20the%20summer.%20We%20conduct%20pilots%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%202%20to%203%20months%20to%20ensure%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20our%20products%20over%20different%20seasons%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20significant%20challenges%20that%20he%20faced%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20information%20among%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20farmers%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20understand%20how%20a%20simple%20light%20could%20deter%20animals%20when%20they%20were%20experiencing%20significant%20problems%20with%20wildlife.%20To%20address%20this%2C%20we%20conducted%20numerous%20demonstrations%20and%20partnered%20with%20organisations%20and%20farmer-produce%20organisations%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAyan%20ran%20pilots%20for%203-6%20months%20in%20various%20areas%2C%20allowing%20farmers%20to%20see%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20their%20solutions%20firsthand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20hands-on%20experience%20helped%20them%20trust%20and%20adopt%20the%20technology.%20Additionally%2C%20there%20was%20a%20general%20lack%20of%20awareness%20among%20farmers%20and%20villagers%20about%20non-invasive%20methods%20to%20deal%20with%20wildlife.%20Many%20were%20inclined%20to%20use%20harmful%20methods%20to%20protect%20their%20crops%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIntroducing%20them%20to%20new%2C%20humane%20technologies%20required%20significant%20effort%20in%20education%20and%20demonstration%20to%20show%20that%20these%20solutions%20could%20be%20effective%20without%20causing%20harm%20to%20the%20animals.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20company%20has%20reached%20and%20collaborated%20with%20more%20than%202%2C000%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307428%2Fhow-did-pathankot-record-just-one-farm-fire-chief-agricultural-officer-dr-amrik-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efarmers%20across%20the%20country%20%3C%2Fa%3Eincluding%20in%20states%20like%20Maharashtra%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Uttrakhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8uVAqPPATd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC8uVAqPPATd%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%2