0you%20get%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20the%20legend%20Beckham%20and%20relay%20your%20dreams%20to%20him.%20But%20Nikhil%20did.%20And%20he%20classifies%20this%20as%20his%20top-tier%20moment%3B%20one%20he%20does%20not%20take%20lightly.%20Retracing%20his%20steps%20leading%20up%20to%20it%2C%20he%20says%20it%20was%20fated.%20%E2%80%9CI%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20planned%20it.%20I%20never%20applied%20to%20UNICEF.%20In%20fact%2C%20I%20applied%20to%20another%20competition%20hosted%20by%20the%20incubation%20centre%20of%20Gujarat%20University%2C%20who%20sent%20my%20project%20to%20UNICEF!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20can%20imagine%20Nikhil%E2%80%99s%20astonishment%20when%20he%20got%20a%20call%20one%20day%20in%20October%202023%20from%20Sanyam%20Chhajed%2C%20programs%20manager%20at%20GUSEC%20(Gujarat%20University%20Startup%20and%20Entrepreneurship%20Council)%2C%20informing%20him%20about%20an%20exhibition%20where%20a%20few%20dignitaries%20would%20be%20present.%20One%20thing%20led%20to%20another%20and%20on%2013%20November%2C%202023%2C%20Nikhil%20was%20one%20of%20five%20chosen%20students%20from%20across%20India%20presenting%20his%20work%20to%20Beckham%2C%20UNICEF%20Goodwill%20Ambassador.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FfYoX20Hz8V8%3Fsi%3DbBW7gjsAVQPnu1P4%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGUSEC%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20his%20journey%2C%20Nikhil%20points%20out%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20has%20received%20immense%20support%20from%20the%20team%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20is%20reciprocal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Chhajed%20shares%2C%20they%20see%20immense%20potential%20in%20Meditel.%20%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20a%20device%20like%20Meditel%20will%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22