d%20to%20spend%20a%20year%20studying.%20He%20referred%20to%20various%20books%20and%20videos%20and%20spoke%20to%20people%20who%20had%20taken%20up%20such%20projects.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20creating%20a%20huge%20pond%20and%20then%20divided%20it%20into%20streams%20throughout%20the%20property.%20This%20water%20became%20the%20main%20source%20of%20water%20for%20life%20to%20flourish%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20created%20six%20more%20ponds%20interconnecting%20them%20with%20the%20main%20one.%20%E2%80%9CI%20then%20planted%20saplings%20of%20trees%20as%20well%20as%20varieties%20of%20tropical%20plants%20I%20collected%20from%20different%20countries%20while%20travelling%20and%20trekking.%20I%20also%20purchased%20a%20few%20around%20the%20ponds%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%205.5%20acres%20of%20once-barren%20land%20now%20houses%20over%202%2C000%20trees%2C%20bamboo%20and%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F298134%2Ffedrick-pariath-transformed-ahmedabad-railway-station-with-solar-energy-water-recycling-waste-management%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20a%20Miyawaki%20forest%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ealong%20with%20hundreds%20of%20fruit%20trees.%20It%20also%20has%20thousands%20of%20tropical%20plants%20seen%20in%20evergreen%20rainforests%2C%20and%20other%20ornamental%20as%20well%20as%20medicinal%20plants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECalm%20in%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20madness%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20bid%20to%20share%20the%20beautiful%20forests%20that%20he%20had%20created%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20Greenara%20Homestay%20was%20born.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4R__0SvdBh%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv